      <title>斯塔默无需大转变就能提高银行和养老金的税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/starmer-can-raise-taxes-on-banks-pensions-without-a-big-u-turn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国反对党工党已排除在7月4日赢得大选后实施大范围增税的可能性，但承诺在少数地方增加税收留有余地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/starmer-can-raise-taxes-on-banks-pensions-without-a-big-u-turn</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 12:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
