    <item>
      <title>法国左翼公布计划，推翻马克龙改革并藐视欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/french-left-unveils-plan-to-undo-macron-s-reforms-and-defy-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国左翼政党联盟提出一份宣言，批评总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙七年来实施的大部分经济改革，并使法国在财政政策问题上与欧盟发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/french-left-unveils-plan-to-undo-macron-s-reforms-and-defy-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京要求乌克兰放弃四个地区进行和谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/putin-demands-ukraine-pull-out-of-four-regions-for-peace-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京呼吁乌克兰从其军队部分占领的四个东部地区撤军，作为和平谈判的条件。在未邀请莫斯科参加的战争会议前夕，基辅方面驳斥了普京的这一要求，称其“带有操纵性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/putin-demands-ukraine-pull-out-of-four-regions-for-peace-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:34:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非各党派同意再次选举拉马福萨为总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-african-unity-government-partners-agree-deal-on-key-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在南非令人震惊的选举结果导致该国失去多数党后，南非政治领导人同意建立广泛联盟来组建下一届政府，并支持西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 再次当选总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-african-unity-government-partners-agree-deal-on-key-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
